  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Village Montana Suites are offered on a bed &amp; breakfast basis or you can upgrade to being on a half board basis. Breakfast, and evening meals for those on half board, is provided each day, drinks are not included.</p>
<p><strong>Please note that on selected dates this hotel is only offered on half board. </strong></p>
<p>Fuel up for the day with a continental buffet breakfast which has a variety of sweet and savoury items, with additional hot options.</p>
<p>Enjoy a seven course evening meal in the Le Gourmet restaurant, with choice of menu and waiter service. Courses include amuse bouche, soup, starter,  main course of fish or meat, cheese, dessert and coffee with pastries.</p>
<p>Dinner can also be booked in the other Village Montana restaurants -La Chaumiere, La Place, L'Aiglon and Chantrelles.  Some dishes may have an additional supplement.</p>
<p>Christmas Dinner and New Years Galas are included.</p>
<p>Earlier meal times for children are available (on request, during French school holidays)</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Compulsory half board dates</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>23rd December </strong></li>
<li><strong>30th December </strong></li>
<li><strong>10th February</strong></li>
<li><strong>17th February</strong></li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
