  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Suites de Montana enjoy an elevated, sunny piste-side location and the hotel is close to the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes Le Lac</a>. Access to the Spa 'Les Bains de Montana' is included, so you can unwind and relax after a day skiing. Little extras in the suites include room service, towels, dressing gowns and slippers and a turndown service.</p>
<h2>Convenient slope access</h2>
<p>Benefitting from having a piste-side location, you can easily access the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a> and with 300km of slopes throughout the domain, you won't be short of areas to explore during your ski holiday. The suites enjoys an elevated and sunny position close to the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a> Le Lac, there's also a shuttle bus on request which runs into the main centre Tignes, so you can easily access the main resort which has plenty of shops, bars and restaurants.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes- Val d'Isere Ski Area</a>, there is nowhere nicer to be than soaking away any aches or pains in a hammam or whirlpool. Guests staying at the suites have access to the spa area 'Les Bains de Montana' which features a heated swimming pool, a sauna, hammam and whirlpool. </p>
<p>The bar and lounge area has a cosy alpine feel, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. It is the perfect spot to enjoy a hot chocolate or cocktail after skiing or before dinner.</p>
<h2>Savoyard specialities</h2>
<p>Treat your taste buds in the Le Gourmet restaurant with its high-end French cuisine and generous selection of delightful cheese and desserts. Guests can also book dinner in the other restaurants which are apart of the Village Montana collection, including the La Chaumiere and Les Chanterelles.</p>]]></description>
