<li>Living room with a fireplace or Austrian stove</li>
<li>Bathroom with a whirlpool bath</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Private Sauna</li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers</li>
